    <string name="theme_info_auto">Auto follows the time of day and switches between focus, playful, serene, and night looks for you.</string>
    <string name="theme_info_focus">Focus keeps the clock cleaner and more work-oriented, with a steadier atmosphere and less playful noise.</string>
    <string name="theme_info_playful">Playful leans brighter and more animated, with more personality in the ambient background and companion layer.</string>
    <string name="theme_info_serene">Serene is the balanced ambient mode: calm, readable, and soft without feeling too quiet.</string>
    <string name="theme_info_night">Night dims the scene, reduces visual pressure, and keeps the clock feeling quieter for late hours.</string>
    <string name="break_reminder_info_on">Break reminders stay silent now. Instead, a soft edge marquee runs around the screen for 10 seconds when it is time to step back.</string>
    <string name="break_reminder_info_off">Break reminders are off. Stopwatch nudges and other long-session rest prompts will stay quiet until you turn this back on.</string>
